dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Bayfield County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads and right of way (ROW) for Bayfield County in 2018. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Bayfield_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are BAYFIELD_ROADS_2018 and BAYFIELD_ROW_2018.
uw_supplemental_s: For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/892/GIS-Data-Downloada
